data.description: Welcome to 727 Fourth Street! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1-car garage house is now available for sale. With ample parking space in your paved driveway, this property offers convenience and comfort for you and your family. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious family room, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The great room features a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere during those chilly evenings. The walkout basement opens onto a covered patio, providing the ideal spot for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air.One of the highlights of this property is the in ground pool, offering endless hours of fun and relaxation during the summer months. The fully fenced-in yard provides privacy and security, making it a safe haven for children and pets to play freely. With a size of 2460 square feet, there is plenty of space to accommodate your growing family's needs. Whether you're looking for a cozy corner to curl up with a book or an area to host memorable gatherings with loved ones, this house has it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home.
